        <p>The Secretary of State makes the following Regulations in exercise of the powers conferred by section 41(1), (2)(a) and (5) of the Road Traffic Act 1988 (the “1988 Act”)().</p>
        <p>Representative organisations have been consulted in accordance with section 195(2) of the 1988 Act.</p>
